## PHASE 6 — How to Update the Dashboard in Future

Whenever you want to add a feature, fix something, or change the design:

1. Go back to Claude (same chat or a new one) and describe what you want, e.g. *"Add a Priority column (High / Medium / Low) to the network table"*
2. Claude gives you updated code
3. Go to **github.com → network-tool → src/App.jsx**
4. Click the **pencil (edit) icon** → select all existing code and delete it → paste Claude's new code
5. Click **Commit changes**
6. Vercel automatically detects the change and redeploys in ~2 minutes
7. Same URL, updated dashboard — your team just refreshes the page

