## Troubleshooting

| Problem | What to do |
|---|---|
| Vercel build fails | Copy the error text from Vercel's build log → paste into Claude → ask it to fix → update `App.jsx` on GitHub |
| Excel upload not working | Tell Claude: *"Excel upload isn't parsing. Use SheetJS, map columns: Function, Sub-Function, Task, Team SPOC, Start Date, End Date, Revised End Date, Total Days, Working Days, Delay Days, Status, Remarks."* |
| Flowchart not showing | Tell Claude: *"React Flow swimlane flowchart isn't rendering. Fix the import and make sure activities are in horizontal swimlanes by Function with red nodes for critical path."* |
| Gantt chart not showing | Tell Claude: *"Recharts Gantt in the Critical Path module isn't rendering. Fix the chart component and handle empty data gracefully."* |
| Inline edits not cascading | Tell Claude: *"When I edit a TAT or date, downstream dates aren't updating. Fix the cascade logic so every cell edit triggers a full recalculation of all dependent dates and the critical path."* |
| App loads blank white page | Vercel → your project → Deployments → latest deployment → copy the build log errors → share with Claude |
| App slow with large Excel | Tell Claude: *"Add loading states and use useMemo to cache network calculations so the app doesn't recalculate on every render."* |

